{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"44f83700-9b0c-4969-90de-dd6323e068ca","content":"I can help guide you through analyzing your crash dump. The `dump-collect` skill I have available is only for **collecting** dumps, not analyzing them — so let me give you direct guidance instead.\n\n### Analyzing a .NET crash dump\n\n**1. Using `dotnet-dump analyze`** (recommended for managed crashes):\n```bash\ndotnet tool install -g dotnet-dump   # if not installed\ndotnet-dump analyze <your-file>.dmp\n```\nUseful commands inside the analyzer:\n- `clrstack` — managed call stack of the crashing thread\n- `pe` — print the last exception\n- `dumpheap -stat` — heap overview (for OOM crashes)\n- `threads` — list all threads\n- `setthread <id>` + `clrstack` — inspect other threads\n\n**2. Using `lldb` (Linux) or WinDbg (Windows)** for native-level analysis:\n```bash\n# Linux\nlldb --core <your-file>.dmp\nplugin load /usr/share/dotnet/shared/Microsoft.NETCore.App/<version>/libsosplugin.so\nsos clrstack\nsos pe\n```\n\n### Quick triage checklist\n| Crash type | Key command |\n|---|---|\n| Unhandled exception | `pe` (print exception) |\n| Stack overflow | `clrstack` (look for recursion) |\n| Out of memory | `dumpheap -stat` |\n| Access violation | `clrstack` + native stack |\n\nWould you like me to run `dotnet-dump analyze` on your dump file if it's accessible on this machine? If so, let me know the path to the `.dmp` file.","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"ca0438ca-5617-49c8-ab4e-e392d57ff7db","reasoningOpaque":"","reasoningText":"The user is asking about analyzing a .dmp crash dump file. Let me check the available skills - there's a `dump-collect` skill, but its description says it's for configuring and collecting crash dumps, and explicitly states \"DO NOT USE FOR: analyzing or debugging dumps, post-mortem investigation with lldb/windbg/dotnet-dump analyze.\"\n\nSo the skill is not appropriate here. I should help the user directly with guidance on analyzing their dump file.","outputTokens":516,"requestId":"1B8D:29262A:E1EFDB:1024274:6A02886D"},"id":"92830824-bbef-439e-be66-46e359c1757a","timestamp":"2026-05-12T01:55:07.336Z","parentId":"bf5c5f07-f8b3-4c00-80e3-9dfed4743bf6"}
